    "Details": "The NDA-2U replaces all the Pulser Laser of the 2K with standard variants, allowing replacing the two MRM-10 with one LRM-15 and one MRM-20. The variant also replaces the ER Large Laser with an ER PPC and drops the Small Laser. The Guardian ECM is further exchanged for a C3 slave computer.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Melee Actuators</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.1</color></b>",
